channel.title: SocNetV | News
channel.description: Social Network Analysis: Social Network Visualizer (SocNetV) is a user-friendly and free software tool for Social Network Analysis and Visualization.

item.title: SocNetV v3.0 Released
item.content:encoded: SocNetV v3.0 is out now! It includes several performance improvements and new features to make social network analysis easier.
